  "html": "<div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ἐπὶ ὑπάτων <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γαΐου · Κεστί\n                    ου Μάρκου Σερουιλίου Νω\n                    νιανοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γαΐου\">Γ(αΐου)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κεστί\n                    ου\">Κεστί-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ου</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μάρκου Σερουιλίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Μάρκου\">Μ(άρκου)</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Σερουιλίου\">Σερουιλίου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Νω\n                    νιανοῦ\">Νω-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>νιανοῦ</span></span> · ἀμφιπόλου δὲ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ἐν Συρακούσαις · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὔλου · Βαλερί\n                    ου Ἀραβικοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Αὔλου\">Α(ὔλου)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Βαλερί\n                    ου\">Βαλερί-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ου</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Ἀραβικοῦ\">Ἀραβικοῦ</span></span> τᾶν δὲ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παί\n                    δων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παί\n                    δων\">Παί-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>δων</span></span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λουκίου · Βηβηίου Κλάδου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\">Λ(ουκίου)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Βηβηίου\">Βηβηίου</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Κλάδου\">Κλάδου</span></span>  <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ἱερείας δὲ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλωδίας Πώλ\n                    λας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κλωδίας\">Κλωδίας</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Πώλ\n                    λας\">Πώλ-<br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>λας</span></span> μηνὸς Πανάμου-<br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>ϛκ´ παρεγένοντο πρὸς <br id=\"al10-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>τὰς <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παῖδας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παῖδας\">Παῖδας</span></span> μετὰ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὐλίας\n                    Τίτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Αὐλίας\">Αὐλί[ας]</span>  <br id=\"al11-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τίτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τίτου\">Τίτου</span></span></span> θυγατέρ[ος] <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φαβία\n                    Σφονγέος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φαβία\">Φαβία</span>  <br id=\"al12-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σφονγέος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"filial\" data-text=\"Σφονγέος\">Σφονγέος</span></span></span> ἡ μήτη[ρ] καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάβιλ\n                    λα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάβιλ\n                    λα\">Φ[άβιλ-]<br id=\"al13-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>λα</span></span> θυγάτηρ καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀπία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπία\">Ἀπία</span></span> [τῇ] <br id=\"al14-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>τριακάδι εὐφρανθ[έντες] <br id=\"al15-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span>καὶ εὐχαριστοῦ&lt;ν&gt;τες <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλ\n                    λωνι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλ\n                    λωνι\">Ἀ[πόλ-]<br id=\"al16-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">16</span>λωνι</span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\">Παίδε[σσι]</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p>"
